    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based<strong> hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a matching lid, with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Peel and roughly chop your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p>",
